Give us a call!
Whether you're a
first-time visitor, veteran camper or just looking around,
we'd love to hear from
you.  Call us at 863-494-1820 or send us an e-mail
to make a reservation,
request further information or give us your feedback.
CRAIG'S RV PARK
7895 NE Cubitis Ave
Arcadia, FL 34266
Phone:
863 494-1820

Meet Our Friendly Staff
The team at CRAIG'S RV PARK welcomes you.
We're here to make your winter stay great.
Everyone has a big job to do,
making sure the office runs smoothly,
keeping things clean, and maintaining the outside.
Each doing their part to provide a nice place to stay.
